{lang-eng}Prabhu vachu varaku kanipettumu nishchayamugaa
Aayana vachunu prabhu raaka nevaru preminthuro
Vaarini prabhuvu konipovunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Aayana raakada sameepamu sahavaasamulo
Nilichi yundi prabhu vaakyamunaku lobadiyu
Aayana korakai kanipettedam{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Adugantu chunnadi aatmeeyatha andari premalu
