Viduvabadina mee gathi yemagun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Thama swantha panulalo viswaasulu kondaru
Nidrinchu chunnaarugaa melconu vaareththa baduduruviduva
Badina vaari gathi yemagun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Novahu kaalamun smariyinthamu samasthamunu
